<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Order Unsuccessful</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #f8f8f8;
			font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
		}
		
		h1 {
			text-align: center;
			margin-top: 50px;
			font-size: 50px;
			color: #222222;
		}
		
		p {
			text-align: center;
			margin-top: 30px;
			font-size: 24px;
			color: #555555;
			line-height: 1.5;
		}
		
		.btn {
			display: inline-block;
			margin-top: 50px;
			padding: 18px 40px;
			border: none;
			background-color: blue;
			color: #ffffff;
			font-size: 24px;
			font-weight: bold;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 1px;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
		}
		
		.btn:hover {
			background-color: blue;
		}
		
		.container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 50px 20px;
		}
		
		@media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
			h1 {
				font-size: 36px;
			}
			
			p {
				font-size: 20px;
			}
			
			.btn {
				padding: 16px 30px;
				font-size: 20px;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>Oops! Something Went Wrong</h1>
		<p>We're sorry, but there was an error processing your order.</p>
		<p>Please try again later, or contact customer support for assistance.</p>
		<a href="/home" class="btn">Back to Shopping</a>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
